Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.73,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,请 请问 这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:51.57,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,稍等一下 我正在热牛奶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.20,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是谁 竟然知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:06.90,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,身体暖和过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.70,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,不用逞强起来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.30,chs for kanon,,0,0,0,,是 没问题的
